00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:46.490
When I started if you would said

00:02:46.490 --> 00:02:49.520
to me would I ever
write an autobiography,

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:52.700
I would have said absolutely not.

00:02:52.700 --> 00:02:56.510
