if I had put down a button

00:03:33.490 --> 00:03:36.610
and I felt sort of lighter.

00:03:36.610 --> 00:03:38.870
And I think this book,
in a way, shows that.

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:43.060
I think it has a kind of lightness
in it which I think has been part

00:03:43.060 --> 00:03:47.990
of the consequence of having got
the autobiography off my chest.

00:03:47.990 --> 00:03:50.320
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: And so, if
