00:06:56.570 --> 00:06:58.010
yeah, genies take Manhattan.

00:06:58.010 --> 00:06:59.680
[ Laughter ]

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:00.980
Three words.

00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:03.720
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: But, you know,
you said something interesting

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:07.740
about while it's not obviously
