00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:30.080
of those children in our century
become the main characters

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:31.380
of the novel.

00:11:31.380 --> 00:11:33.860
And the other thing that
was going to happen is

00:11:33.860 --> 00:11:38.240
