of the worlds as described

00:13:09.830 --> 00:13:11.980
in the book is a war
between the age of--

00:13:11.980 --> 00:13:14.250
between reason and unreason
as you described it.

00:13:14.250 --> 00:13:15.550
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Yeah.

00:13:15.550 --> 00:13:17.910 position:56%
Well, what the book suggests is that
the book begins or the modern part

00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:22.500
of the book begins
with a huge storm,

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:25.650
a kind of super Hurricane Sandy.

00:13:25.650 --> 00:13:30.250
And this storm, it
suggests it's so powerful

00:13:30.250 --> 00:13:35.210
that it breaks open the seals which
separate our world form the world

00:13:35.210 --> 00:13:38.120
of these supernatural
beings, the jinn.

00:13:38.120 --> 00:13:41.450
And the jinn pour through
the cracks.

00:13:41.450 --> 00:13:46.840
And some of them are really very
bad and wanted to take over.

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:48.140
And they're very powerful.

00:13:48.140 --> 00:13:51.520
