00:14:02.160 --> 00:14:03.460
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Yeah.

00:14:03.460 --> 00:14:04.760
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Yeah.

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:06.760
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Yeah, I
mean, actually with Jeff for PBS

00:14:06.760 --> 00:14:09.770
