ISIS, you know what I mean?

00:14:52.510 --> 00:14:56.220
That time, Isis was the
name of an Egyptian goddess.

00:14:56.220 --> 00:14:58.490
And that was all.

00:14:58.490 --> 00:15:04.940
And so, when I started describing
this war taking place in, you know,

00:15:04.940 --> 00:15:10.490
in what the novel calls Mesopotamia
but we what we know better as Iraq,

00:15:10.490 --> 00:15:14.910
there was no such war taking place.

00:15:14.910 --> 00:15:18.960
And then just as I was getting
to the end of the novel,

00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:22.090
you know, it started happening.

00:15:22.090 --> 00:15:23.690
And that was alarming.

00:15:23.690 --> 00:15:26.360
I would like my books
to stop coming through.

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:30.170
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: I mean, but given
