00:20:08.180 --> 00:20:14.830
Enough. I'm just going to
do this old fashion thing.

00:20:14.830 --> 00:20:16.130
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Write novels?

00:20:16.130 --> 00:20:17.430
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Writing books.

00:20:17.430 --> 00:20:18.730
Yeah.

00:20:18.730 --> 00:20:20.030
