00:23:42.910 --> 00:23:44.210
And--

00:23:44.210 --> 00:23:45.510
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Yeah.

00:23:45.510 --> 00:23:46.810
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: And it has
