00:29:58.170 --> 00:30:00.570
all of that has fed directly

00:30:00.570 --> 00:30:03.480
into the mainstream of
American literature.

00:30:04.850 --> 00:30:10.040
Now, in a generation
much younger than mine,

00:30:10.040 --> 00:30:11.870
there are new American writers

00:30:11.870 --> 00:30:14.550
from really almost
everywhere in the world.

00:30:14.550 --> 00:30:17.310
You know, there's Junot Diaz
