00:31:08.500 --> 00:31:12.910
And now, I genuinely
think that this generation

00:31:12.910 --> 00:31:17.550
of new migrant stories arriving
in American literature is one

00:31:17.550 --> 00:31:20.200 position:56%
of the best things to happen to
American literature for a long time.

00:31:20.200 --> 00:31:22.000
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Well, it's
