00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.700
Anyway, I thought it
was pretty good.

00:32:27.700 --> 00:32:29.510
My father lost it.

00:32:29.510 --> 00:32:30.810
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: No.

00:32:30.810 --> 00:32:32.110
Salman Rushdie: Yeah.

00:32:32.110 --> 00:32:34.360
My father said you won't be able to
look after it, I'll look after it.

00:32:34.360 --> 00:32:37.170
And then he lost it.

00:32:37.170 --> 00:32:40.230 position:56%
