00:34:30.430 --> 00:34:37.840
There was this little theater in
Cambridge called The Arts Cinema,

00:34:37.840 --> 00:34:43.560 position:56%
which like everything else no longer
exist and now it's a coffee shop.

00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:47.840
But I feel I got my education
in that little room, you know,

00:34:47.840 --> 00:34:52.800
watching, you know, Godard's
