00:34:57.280 --> 00:35:00.190
"Exterminating Angel",
and so on, you know?

00:35:00.190 --> 00:35:03.520
And I think those-- those
things have a colossal--

00:35:03.520 --> 00:35:07.500
this book is in incredibly
influenced by those films.

00:35:07.500 --> 00:35:09.350
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: And
there's the golden--

00:35:09.350 --> 00:35:11.080
so-called the golden age
of television [inaudible].

00:35:11.080 --> 00:35:13.700
Well, are you watching
a lot of these series?

00:35:13.700 --> 00:35:15.000
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Oh, this, yeah.

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:16.300
I mean, I'm interested.

00:35:16.300 --> 00:35:19.190
I'm interested because
it's clear that this thing,

00:35:19.190 --> 00:35:24.990
this new form of the
60-minute drama series,

00:35:24.990 --> 00:35:26.940
