00:39:27.020 --> 00:39:33.330
You know, you don't need all those
they call them campuses, you know?

00:39:33.330 --> 00:39:34.630
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Google--

00:39:34.630 --> 00:39:35.930
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie:
Google, Microsoft,

00:39:35.930 --> 00:39:37.280
all of that, they're
