OK, yeah.

00:40:05.950 --> 00:40:07.250
&gt;&gt; Is that OK?

00:40:07.250 --> 00:40:10.470
OK. So, you said that in drawing
the distinction between the person

00:40:10.470 --> 00:40:14.210
who sits down to write a novel and
the person who takes to Twitter

00:40:14.210 --> 00:40:17.630
that there sort of
needs to be truths

00:40:17.630 --> 00:40:19.820
so that the novelist
