00:40:27.740 --> 00:40:30.420
what is it that's left
for the novelist to do

00:40:30.420 --> 00:40:33.210
or how are the fabrications of
the novelist suppose to differ

00:40:33.210 --> 00:40:35.830
from the fabrications
of the Twitter user

00:40:35.830 --> 00:40:38.560
or the spectacularized politician?

00:40:38.560 --> 00:40:41.240
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: Well,
it's a question, you know?

00:40:41.240 --> 00:40:42.540
There's no doubt.

00:40:42.540 --> 00:40:44.270
I mean, the answer is you got
to deal with it, you know?

00:40:44.270 --> 00:40:47.610
I think what happens, is the
world changes all the time

00:40:47.610 --> 00:40:49.820 position:56%
and the novel has to change with it.

00:40:49.820 --> 00:40:58.800
And one of the things that's
happened now, is that reality

00:40:58.800 --> 00:41:01.790
or what we consider to be
reality has become very contested.

00:41:01.790 --> 00:41:04.300
There's isn't an agreement
about what it is.

00:41:04.300 --> 00:41:07.610 position:56%
You know, whereas, if you think
about the great heyday of the novel,

00:41:07.610 --> 00:41:09.900
think about, you know,
the 19th century novel,

00:41:09.900 --> 00:41:14.420
the 19th century realist novel,
that was based essentially

00:41:14.420 --> 00:41:17.830
on the knowledge that the
writer had, that the writer

00:41:17.830 --> 00:41:21.180
and the reader would basically
have the same picture of the world.

00:41:21.180 --> 00:41:23.250
You know, they would
basically see the world

00:41:23.250 --> 00:41:25.860
in the same way as
being the same thing.

00:41:25.860 --> 00:41:29.990
And out of that agreement
between the writer and the reader,

00:41:29.990 --> 00:41:31.290
came the realist tradition.

00:41:31.290 --> 00:41:33.800
You know, it's built
on that agreement.

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:35.260
But if you now live in a time

00:41:35.260 --> 00:41:39.680
in which reality has become
incredibly contested and disputed

00:41:39.680 --> 00:41:44.500
and messed around with, it's
very hard to write that kind

00:41:44.500 --> 00:41:48.470
of realist novel, because that
agreement no longer exists,

00:41:48.470 --> 00:41:49.770
you know?

00:41:49.770 --> 00:41:51.070
So, you have to think
of different forms.

00:41:51.070 --> 00:41:54.470
I mean, that's what I think
many of us are wrestling with.

