and I think his government is
a very alarming government.

00:54:58.480 --> 00:55:02.990
And I do think it's
frightening for people, you know.

00:55:02.990 --> 00:55:04.490
Self-censorship, I can't tell.

00:55:04.490 --> 00:55:09.280
