to me to be the greatest crime

00:55:09.280 --> 00:55:11.340
that a writer can commit.

00:55:11.340 --> 00:55:16.300
I mean, if you feel that
scared, then don't write.

00:55:16.300 --> 00:55:19.100
Nobody is asking you
to write, you know?

00:55:19.100 --> 00:55:22.970 position:56%
And if you-- if by writing, you
