00:56:23.230 --> 00:56:24.530
&gt;&gt; Bilal Qureshi: Selective.

00:56:24.530 --> 00:56:27.990
&gt;&gt; So, what do you say to that?

00:56:27.990 --> 00:56:29.890
&gt;&gt; Salman Rushdie: You'll
